Device Types

Device Types : Codes used to identify medical devices. This value set includes all children of SNOMED CT Concepts (US Extension and Core) from SCTID 49062001 Device (physical object) and is provided as a suggestive example.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include codes from http://snomed.info/sct where concept is-a 49062001 (Device)
